NAME        glycerol-1-phosphatase;
            alpha-glycerophosphatase;
            alpha-glycerol phosphatase;
            glycerol 3-phosphatase;
            glycerol-3-phosphate phosphatase;
            glycerol 3-phosphate phosphohydrolase
CLASS       Hydrolases;
